items.storedetaileddescription: Walker Tape®’s Brushes are designed to help you offer safe and sanitary services to multiple clients. They evenly spread adhesives, solvents, or preparation product on the scalp. A great single-use option for stylists to prevent cross-contamination while using other products.
items.outofstockbehavior: Allow back orders with no out-of-stock message
